        <title>MOUNTING AND LINKAGE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Check for and correct loose, bent or broken shock absorber mountings and linkage when
                servicing the suspension system.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Inspect all rubber bushings and grommets to see that they prevent metal-to-metal contact.
